high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the stove.
Put the knife in a pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Put the pot on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot with a knife to the round table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and move back to the counter, face to the left side.
Pick up the knife from the front edge of the counter.
Hold the knife and move a few steps left to the stove.
Place the knife inside the pot on the back left burner.
Pick up the pot from the back left burner.
Carry the pot and turn around. Move forward and then turn left to find the white table.
Place the pot on the far back right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot and knife to the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with a knife in it on the stove.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Place the pan with a knife in it on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a pan and place it on the kitchen table.
